frames.caption: A figure with a dinosaur head walks confidently down a fashion runway, wearing a black leather jacket adorned with metal studs and intricate tattoos covering its legs. The scene is set under dramatic lighting, highlighting the unique blend of prehistoric and modern punk aesthetics.
frames.description: The scene takes place at a fashion show, where a model is dressed in an avant-garde outfit combining elements of punk fashion with a dinosaur-themed headpiece. The atmosphere is bold and unconventional, emphasizing creativity and individuality.

frames.caption: A person dressed in a dinosaur costume walks down a fashion runway. The costume features a leather jacket and boots, adding a unique twist to the prehistoric theme. The audience is seated on either side, observing the spectacle.
frames.description: The scene is set at a fashion show runway where a person in a dinosaur costume is the main attraction. The costume combines elements of prehistoric and modern fashion with its leather jacket and boots.
